{
  "stem": "1704.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you stayed, you had to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember also where, read beans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call it reading, you know, sorting them out, beans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe for factory or something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did that for a little while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's about all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think he did anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a couple of years younger than I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was not quite-- how would I say-- handicapped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not normal, but not bad either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe these days they would call it ADD, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Attention deficiency.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These days, they would have been able to help him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But those days-- that's why he died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wouldn't stand to camp life, missed the parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Westerbork, and later in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing really, just keep an eye on him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he couldn't keep a secret Well, you know, he'd blabber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- it's very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had friends that tried to look after.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The men there helped him shave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they helped to look after him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, you could trust each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were not different nationalities-- nothing-- not in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just Dutch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Dutch and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, there was a bit of a hate for the Germans, even though they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they had preference above us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From June '43 until January '44.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 23.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Passenger train, it was all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when we arrived, we thought, a good camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And straightaway, we saw the SS, with the cross and bone, that regiment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember the 7 o'clock in the morning, far away, we heard a church bell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was so quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a truck standing ready.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
